
        ****For Loop***** 
        Syntax: 
        for(initialization;condition;increment/decrement){
        stmts.....    
        }

        ****While Loop*****
        Syntax:
        initialize looping variable
         while(condition){
         stmt;
         increment/decrement;
         }
        
         ****Do-While****/
        Syntax:
         initialization

        do{
             stmt;
             increment/decrement
        }while(condition)